xss
-----------

A simple X11 screenshot utility. It writes farbfeld image data to stdout.


Build and install
-----------------

$ make
# make install


Dependencies
------------

- libX11


Optional dependencies
---------------------

- To convert farbfeld data you can use ff2jpg or ff2png from:
  https://git.suckless.org/farbfeld/


Usage
-----

xscreenshot > file.ff
ff2png < file.ff > file.png


Known issues
------------

A specified windowid has to be visible on the screen.
